title: Bug 121687: Exception thrown when exporting data from a table inside a grid cell
description: When attempting to export data from a table that is placed inside a grid cell, an exception is thrown.
OB: When trying to export data from a table inside a grid cell, an exception is thrown.
EB: Exporting data from a table inside a grid cell should not throw an exception.
SR:
To reproduce the issue, follow these steps:
1. Insert a table into one of the grid cells.
2. Insert another table into the other grid cell.
3. Attempt to export data from one of the tables.
4. Observe the exception being thrown.
